{"prompt": "Build a portfolio for a freelance illustrator. The overall look should be imaginative, incorporating a creamy yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elara Vance - Freelance Illustrator</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fdf5e6; /* Creamy yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf5e6, #fcebb6); /* Creamy yellow to a lighter shade */\n            color: #4a3b3b;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid #d4ac0d; /* A slightly deeper yellow/gold */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n            color: #6b5a5a;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #fcebb6;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #4a3b3b;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #d4ac0d;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #fffaf0; /* Off-white */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #a08550; /* Warm, earthy tone */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #d4ac0d;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        #about img {\n            display: block;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            width: 150px;\n            height: 150px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border: 5px solid #fdf5e6;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item {\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 300px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item .overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(74, 59, 59, 0.7); /* Darker warm tone overlay */\n            color: #fff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n            padding: 15px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item:hover .overlay {\n            opacity: 1;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item .overlay h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        #portfolio .gallery-item .overlay p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        #contact label {\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #6b5a5a;\n        }\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #d4ac0d;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            background-color: #fffaf0;\n            color: #333;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        #contact textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        #contact button {\n            background-color: #d4ac0d;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #a08550;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #fcebb6;\n            color: #4a3b3b;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-top: 2px solid #d4ac0d;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .hidden {\n            display: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elara Vance</h1>\n        <p>Weaving tales through ink and color.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/fdf5e6/4a3b3b?text=EV\" alt=\"Elara Vance - Illustrator\">\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 20px auto;\">\n                Hello! I'm Elara, a freelance illustrator with a passion for creating whimsical and imaginative worlds. My work often draws inspiration from nature, folklore, and the magic found in everyday moments. I specialize in digital illustration, character design, and vibrant editorial pieces. Let's bring your vision to life with a touch of wonder!\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Portfolio Highlights</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fdf5e6/4a3b3b?text=Enchanted+Forest\" alt=\"Enchanted Forest Illustration\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\">\n                        <h3>Enchanted Forest</h3>\n                        <p>Digital painting, nature-inspired.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fcebb6/4a3b3b?text=Character+Design\" alt=\"Character Design Art\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\">\n                        <h3>Character Designs</h3>\n                        <p>Vibrant character concepts for games.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fdf5e6/4a3b3b?text=Mythical+Creature\" alt=\"Mythical Creature Illustration\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\">\n                        <h3>Mythical Creature</h3>\n                        <p>Fantasy illustration, detailed.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fcebb6/4a3b3b?text=Editorial+Illustration\" alt=\"Editorial Illustration\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\">\n                        <h3>Editorial Piece</h3>\n                        <p>Illustrating for a magazine article.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fdf5e6/4a3b3b?text=Whimsical+Scene\" alt=\"Whimsical Scene Illustration\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\">\n                        <h3>Whimsical Scene</h3>\n                        <p>A touch of everyday magic.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/fcebb6/4a3b3b?text=Book+Illustration\" alt=\"Book Illustration\">\n                    <div class=\"overlay\">\n                        <h3>Children's Book</h3>\n                        <p>Illustrations for a storybook.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elara Vance. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! I will get back to you soon.');\n            // In a real application, you would send this data to a server here.\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}